channel.title: ~~~ [317] Flamed Fury [317] My first server! 370+ Downloads! ~~~
channel.description:
Ok, first off, before you all say I suck, I just want to let you know this is my first server source and it would be nice if you would give me GOOD and NICE feedback and no put downs! Thanks!
[size=14pt]Be sure to comment on this post with your opinion!! COMMENT ON THIS TO KEEP THE POST ALIVE![/size] I think I'm going to quit private servers b/c they're illegal so good bye everyone! Take care of my wondrous work of java coding!
Download link: http://uppit.com/v/H3YUAJ6N
[size=24pt]~YOU MUST READ THIS~[/size] If you download and you leech me, GIVE ME CREDITS! And also when you dl there's a folder called "Other" and it has 4 documents. 1. Silab Item Codes 2. A README.txt document so [size=24pt][b]READ[/b][/size] that! I know, I know, you're probably thinking 'I hate reading!' but just spare a minute of your time to read it. 3. A Updates documents 4. A Coordinates document
~ Credits ~ Me Zykev2 for CryptchaosV3 source!! Hidden Pker `Rich o.O O.o
[size=16pt]~~FEATURES!~~[/size] Cleaned Chatlogs.txt Changed staff area Relocated the JAD Fixed NPC Drops! Working Report System! More NPCs added to train! New FunPK Area! New Home area New starting outfit Starter has been changed New Thieve area New Smithing/Mining area Another new mining area!
